      <title>韩国计划于 3 月份解除对所有股票的卖空禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/south-korea-aims-to-end-short-selling-ban-on-all-stocks-in-march</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国最高金融监管机构表示，计划在 3 月底解除卖空禁令，并将确保届时完成必要的规则修订。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/south-korea-aims-to-end-short-selling-ban-on-all-stocks-in-march</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
