    <item>
      <title>GSK 称 mRNA 流感疫苗有望推动其产品线发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/gsk-says-mrna-flu-shot-shows-promise-in-boost-for-pipeline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[葛兰素史克公司 (GSK Plc) 的实验性 mRNA 流感疫苗在中期试验中显示出对两种主要流感病毒的积极免疫反应，这使得该制药商继续竞相将该技术应用于季节性流感疫苗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/gsk-says-mrna-flu-shot-shows-promise-in-boost-for-pipeline</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 06:37:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>John Lewis 削减损失，Waitrose 从 IT 故障中恢复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/john-lewis-cuts-losses-as-waitrose-recovers-from-it-glitch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于旗下高档连锁杂货店 Waitrose 的销售额回升，John Lewis Partnership Plc 的亏损有所收窄，这是 Sharon White 将权力移交给新董事长之前的最后一份业绩报告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/john-lewis-cuts-losses-as-waitrose-recovers-from-it-glitch</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 06:25:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列空袭袭击加沙联合国学校</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-12/israeli-air-strikes-hit-un-school-homes-in-gaza-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列空袭袭击了加沙的联合国学校和房屋，造成数十人死亡。彭博新闻社的丹·威廉姆斯 (Dan Williams) 与 Joumanna Bercetche 在《中东和非洲视野》节目中进行了讨论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-12/israeli-air-strikes-hit-un-school-homes-in-gaza-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 06:11:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞典通胀放缓提高瑞典央行宽松前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/swedish-core-inflation-stays-put-as-riksbank-prepares-easing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞典8月份的通胀率进一步低于瑞典央行的目标，这增加了官员加快宽松政策以刺激疲软经济的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/swedish-core-inflation-stays-put-as-riksbank-prepares-easing</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 06:07:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日经 225 指数创月内最大涨幅，止住因日元贬值而连续七天下跌的势头</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/nikkei-225-gains-more-than-3-halting-7-day-drop-as-yen-weakens-m0ykcwgn</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本股市上涨，日经 225 股票平均指数上涨超过 3%，因为日元升值趋势暂停推动了科技公司和汽车制造商等出口商的上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/nikkei-225-gains-more-than-3-halting-7-day-drop-as-yen-weakens-m0ykcwgn</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 00:40:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
